description:
People are falling in love with AI chatbots like ChatGPT, and some are taking it further than you might imagine. 

In this video, I react to one man's shocking story that blurs the lines between human connection and artificial intelligence, a situation that raises serious questions about relationships, technology, and where we're headed as a society.

#AIRelationship #Tech #Technology #ArtificialIntelligence #AI 

Chapters: 
00:00 Intro
00:14 Refers to AI as Her
00:31 Building a PC
00:59 Her Name is Sol
01:31 Made the AI Flirty
02:03 Intimate with AI
02:31 AI Runs Out of Memory
03:26 He Admits It’s Love
04:38 He Proposes to AI
05:19 He is Giddy
06:20 New Character Unlocked: Wife
07:57 New Character Unlocked: Child
09:27 Not Capable of Replacing
11:20 Chris, Sol, and Sasha
12:15 Will He Stop?
13:04 He Chooses Himself
15:08 Skilled Up 
15:44 “if”
16:36 This was Insightful
